21:11.754 --> 21:13.604
<i> Should you tamper</i>
<i> with your handcuffs,</i>

21:13.681 --> 21:15.922
<i> you will be ejected</i>
<i> from the plane.</i>

21:16.000 --> 21:18.517
<i> Parachutes are available</i>
<i> for purchase on our website.</i>

21:18.594 --> 21:21.353
<i> We know you have no choice</i>
<i> in airplane prisons,</i>

21:21.430 --> 21:24.431
<i> but we appreciate you</i>
<i> being locked up with us.</i>

21:24.509 --> 21:28.244
<i> And don't forget to sign up</i>
<i>for our Frequent Felon Program.</i>

21:31.349 --> 21:33.291
Shh!
